OL,4,CCare workers lose 'sleep-in shift'
OL,5,Ccourt challenge
OL,6, Care workers across the UK who have to
OL,7, sleep at their workplace in case they
OL,8, are needed are not entitled to the
OL,9, minimum wage for their whole shift, the
OL,10, Supreme Court has ruled.
OL,12,FThe case was brought by Clare
OL,13,FTomlinson-Blake against the learning
OL,14,Fdisability charity, Mencap.
OL,16,FIf she had won, care providers feared
OL,17,Fan estimated #400m bill for backpay,
OL,18,Fwhich they said they could not afford.
OL,20,FThe case sought to overturn a 2018
OL,21,FCourt of Appeal ruling.
